platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Convinced you’ve run out of things to watch? Amazon Prime Video may be able to prove otherwise. The app is brimming with brilliant films, dramas, and comedies, as well as sports and children’s TV, all available to watch on demand. We love the ultra-high-quality 4K streaming and the slick UI. Oh, and the ability to create multiple user profiles and download series to watch later. There are also hundreds of Amazon Originals to check out—great series and films produced by Amazon Studios that you won’t find anywhere else.
正在尋找更多出色節目觀看？這個 App 匯聚精彩電影、劇集、喜劇，以及體育和兒童電視節目，讓你隨時想睇就睇。
Convinced you’ve run out of things to watch? This app is brimming with brilliant films, dramas, and comedies, as well as sports and children’s TV, all available to watch on demand.
観たい作品に困ったら、このアプリをチェックしてみてください。数え切れないほどの素晴らしい映画やドラマ、コメディ、スポーツ、家族で楽しめるテレビ番組などを、すべてオンデマンドで視聴できます。
這款 App 提供豐富影劇內容，包括體育和兒童節目，隨時隨地滿足你的娛樂需求，讓你再也不愁沒東西可看。
Vous n’avez plus rien à regarder ? Cette app regorge de films, de drames et de comédies remarquables, mais aussi de programmes sportifs et pour enfants, tous disponibles à la demande.
